The '''Shiritoku Way''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] running through the [[Shiritoku Spur]] on the edges of the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] and [[Wild Space/Legends|Wild Space]]. The route ran through the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Timora]].

